## FastAPI API Contracts

All endpoints are prefixed with `/api/v1`. Request/response bodies are JSON.

---

### Module 1 — Knowledge Base

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|--------|----------|---------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/knowledge-base` | Fetch the saved company info |
| `PUT` | `/api/v1/knowledge-base` | Save/update the company info text |

**`GET /api/v1/knowledge-base`** → Response:
```json
{
  "content": "We are a B2B SaaS company...",
  "updated_at": "2026-03-06T14:00:00Z"
}
```

**`PUT /api/v1/knowledge-base`** → Request body:
```json
{
  "content": "We are a B2B SaaS company..."
}
```
Response: `{ "status": "saved", "updated_at": "..." }`

---

### Module 2 — Workflows

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|--------|----------|---------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/workflows` | List all saved workflows |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/workflows/{id}` | Get a single workflow by ID |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/workflows` | Create a new workflow |
| `PUT` | `/api/v1/workflows/{id}` | Update an existing workflow |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/workflows/{id}` | Delete a workflow |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/workflows/{id}/test` | Run a test simulation |

**`POST /api/v1/workflows`** → Request:
```json
{
  "name": "Cold Outreach",
  "description": "Initial cold outreach sequence",
  "nodes": [
    { "id": "1", "type": "trigger", "position": { "x": 0, "y": 100 }, "data": {} },
    { "id": "2", "type": "ai_generate", "position": { "x": 200, "y": 100 }, "data": {} }
  ],
  "edges": [
    { "id": "e1-2", "source": "1", "target": "2" }
  ]
}
```

**`POST /api/v1/workflows/{id}/test`** → Request:
```json
{
  "persona": "skeptical_cto",
  "lead_name": "John Smith"
}
```
Response: Returns a `workflow_run` with `id` that can be polled for status.

