### Module 3 — Dashboard

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|--------|----------|---------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/stats` | Aggregated counts (total, active, completed, failed) |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/runs` | List of workflow runs with current status |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/logs` | Execution log entries (most recent first) |

**`GET /api/v1/dashboard/stats`** → Response:
```json
{
  "total_runs": 24,
  "active": 3,
  "completed": 18,
  "failed": 3
}
```

**`GET /api/v1/dashboard/runs`** → Response:
```json
{
  "runs": [
    {
      "id": "run-uuid",
      "lead_name": "John Smith",
      "workflow_name": "Cold Outreach",
      "current_step": "Follow-up Email",
      "status": "waiting",
      "started_at": "2026-03-06T10:00:00Z"
    }
  ]
}
```

**`GET /api/v1/dashboard/logs`** → Response:
```json
{
  "logs": [
    {
      "timestamp": "2026-03-06T10:01:00Z",
      "lead_name": "John Smith",
      "event": "Email Generated",
      "log_type": "info"
    }
  ]
}
```

