## Sprint Deliverables — What Will Be Achieved

By the end of this backend sprint, the system will support:

| # | Deliverable | Description |
|---|-------------|-------------|
| 1 | **Persistent Knowledge Base** | Company info saved to DB, loads on page refresh |
| 2 | **Workflow CRUD** | Create, read, update, delete workflows via API |
| 3 | **Workflow Test Runner** | Hit "Test" on a workflow → simulated execution against a persona, generating run records and logs |
| 4 | **Live Dashboard** | Dashboard pulls real data from DB instead of hardcoded mock data |
| 5 | **Execution Logging** | Every step of a test run creates timestamped log entries |
| 6 | **Frontend ↔ Backend Wired** | Frontend pages will call real API endpoints instead of using local state/mock data |

> [!NOTE]
> AI message generation (the actual LLM call in the AI Generate node) is **not** part of this sprint. The test runner will use **simulated/templated responses** for now. LLM integration will be a separate sprint.
